{
  "stem": "7684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she came from-- her-- her husband had a very big factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was very rich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she got smuggled in all different things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She bought up the people that brought food to us and things like that-- I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because she got all different kinds of things in-- in to the-- to the jail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember-- she was very-- a woman from-- from the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and I found her later in Vught, in another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was together already with the head of the-- from the-- from the-- a Jewish man, but had also something to say.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she was a very impressive person-- and would every morning exercise, and things like that, in jail.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- the spirit was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nobody knows about gas chambers, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I guess because we were Jews, our religion-- and we were born as Jew, we were in this-- in jail.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- we didn't think that would something serious would happen to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't get much to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember once, the woman what brought us the food said to me, gee, you look so familiar.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you have a brother that was a waiter in-- in a hotel?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my oldest brother was in hotel school and had to work in an-- in a hotel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, through that, we got double food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got more food then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was luck in-- in jail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there out, we came together in-- in January, we came together in an office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came together with a whole bunch of Dutch girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is 1943.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or 19--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 1942-- end of 1942-- beginning of 1943, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
